{
  "video_id": "vC1uxXvPG0Q",
  "title": "Pirates, nurses and other rebel designers | Alice Rawsthorn",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12875.0,
      "end_time": 15921.0,
      "text": "Design is a slippery and elusive phenomenon,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15921.0,
      "end_time": 19206.0,
      "text": "which has meant different things at different times."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 19206.0,
      "end_time": 23498.0,
      "text": "But all truly inspiring design projects have one thing in common:"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 23498.0,
      "end_time": 25679.0,
      "text": "they began with a dream."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 25679.0,
      "end_time": 27141.0,
      "text": "And the bolder the dream,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 27141.0,
      "end_time": 30806.0,
      "text": "the greater the design feat that will be required to achieve it."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 30806.0,
      "end_time": 34724.0,
      "text": "And this is why the greatest designers are almost always"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 34724.0,
      "end_time": 38787.0,
      "text": "the biggest dreamers and rebels and renegades."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 38787.0,
      "end_time": 41594.0,
      "text": "This has been the case throughout history,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 41594.0,
      "end_time": 45539.0,
      "text": "all the way back to the year 300 BC,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 45539.0,
      "end_time": 48682.0,
      "text": "when a 13-year-old became the king"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 48682.0,
      "end_time": 53475.0,
      "text": "of a remote, very poor and very small Asian country."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 53475.0,
      "end_time": 56984.0,
      "text": "He dreamt of acquiring land, riches and power"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 56984.0,
      "end_time": 58675.0,
      "text": "through military conquest."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 58675.0,
      "end_time": 60082.0,
      "text": "And his design skills --"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 60082.0,
      "end_time": 61929.0,
      "text": "improbable though it sounds --"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 61929.0,
      "end_time": 65605.0,
      "text": "would be essential in enabling him to do so."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 65605.0,
      "end_time": 66779.0,
      "text": "At the time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 66779.0,
      "end_time": 70213.0,
      "text": "all weapons were made by hand to different specifications."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 70213.0,
      "end_time": 73543.0,
      "text": "So if an archer ran out of arrows during a battle,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 73543.0,
      "end_time": 77490.0,
      "text": "they wouldn&#39;t necessarily be able to fire another archer&#39;s arrows"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 77490.0,
      "end_time": 79362.0,
      "text": "from their bow."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 79362.0,
      "end_time": 82947.0,
      "text": "This of course meant that they would be less effective in combat"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 82947.0,
      "end_time": 85339.0,
      "text": "and very vulnerable, too."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 85339.0,
      "end_time": 86965.0,
      "text": "Ying solved this problem"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 86965.0,
      "end_time": 91080.0,
      "text": "by insisting that all bows and arrows were designed identically,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 91080.0,
      "end_time": 92835.0,
      "text": "so they were interchangeable."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 92835.0,
      "end_time": 96861.0,
      "text": "And he did the same for daggers, axes, spears, shields"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 96861.0,
      "end_time": 100002.0,
      "text": "and every other form of weaponry."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 100002.0,
      "end_time": 103932.0,
      "text": "His formidably equipped army won batter after battle,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 103932.0,
      "end_time": 105746.0,
      "text": "and within 15 years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 105746.0,
      "end_time": 108928.0,
      "text": "his tiny kingdom had succeeded in conquering"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 108928.0,
      "end_time": 111777.0,
      "text": "all its larger, richer, more powerful neighbors,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 111777.0,
      "end_time": 115041.0,
      "text": "to found the mighty Chinese Empire."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 115041.0,
      "end_time": 116594.0,
      "text": "Now, no one, of course,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 116594.0,
      "end_time": 120396.0,
      "text": "would have thought of describing Ying Zheng as a designer at the time --"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 120396.0,
      "end_time": 121628.0,
      "text": "why would they?"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 121628.0,
      "end_time": 125455.0,
      "text": "And yet he used design unknowingly and instinctively"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 125455.0,
      "end_time": 127439.0,
      "text": "but with tremendous ingenuity"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 127439.0,
      "end_time": 129631.0,
      "text": "to achieve his ends."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 129631.0,
      "end_time": 134195.0,
      "text": "And so did another equally improbable, accidental designer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 134195.0,
      "end_time": 138376.0,
      "text": "who was also not above using violence to get what he wanted."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 138376.0,
      "end_time": 144012.0,
      "text": "This was Edward Teach, better known as the British pirate, Blackbeard."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 144012.0,
      "end_time": 146301.0,
      "text": "This was the golden age of piracy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 146301.0,
      "end_time": 149998.0,
      "text": "where pirates like Teach were terrorizing the high seas."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 149998.0,
      "end_time": 151991.0,
      "text": "Colonial trade was flourishing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 151991.0,
      "end_time": 154276.0,
      "text": "and piracy was highly profitable."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 154276.0,
      "end_time": 159139.0,
      "text": "And the smarter pirates like him realized that to maximize their spoils,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 159139.0,
      "end_time": 163790.0,
      "text": "they needed to attack their enemies so brutally"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 163790.0,
      "end_time": 165607.0,
      "text": "that they would surrender on sight."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 165607.0,
      "end_time": 166782.0,
      "text": "So in other words,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 166782.0,
      "end_time": 169352.0,
      "text": "they could take the ships without wasting ammunition,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 169352.0,
      "end_time": 171417.0,
      "text": "or incurring casualties."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 171417.0,
      "end_time": 175106.0,
      "text": "So Edward Teach redesigned himself as Blackbeard"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 175106.0,
      "end_time": 177794.0,
      "text": "by playing the part of a merciless brute."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 177794.0,
      "end_time": 181843.0,
      "text": "He wore heavy jackets and big hats to accentuate his height."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 181843.0,
      "end_time": 185362.0,
      "text": "He grew the bushy black beard that obscured his face."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 185362.0,
      "end_time": 188933.0,
      "text": "He slung braces of pistols on either shoulder."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 188933.0,
      "end_time": 192855.0,
      "text": "He even attached matches to the brim of his hat and set them alight,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 192855.0,
      "end_time": 197009.0,
      "text": "so they sizzled menacingly whenever his ship was poised to attack."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 197009.0,
      "end_time": 199605.0,
      "text": "And like many pirates of that era,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 199605.0,
      "end_time": 202518.0,
      "text": "he flew a flag that bore the macabre symbols"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 202518.0,
      "end_time": 206002.0,
      "text": "of a human skull and a pair of crossed bones,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 206002.0,
      "end_time": 211717.0,
      "text": "because those motifs had signified death in so many cultures for centuries,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 211717.0,
      "end_time": 214603.0,
      "text": "that their meaning was instantly recognizable,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 214603.0,
      "end_time": 218167.0,
      "text": "even in the lawless, illiterate world of the high seas:"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 218167.0,
      "end_time": 220667.0,
      "text": "surrender or you&#39;ll suffer."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 220667.0,
      "end_time": 224646.0,
      "text": "So of course, all his sensible victims surrendered on sight."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 224646.0,
      "end_time": 226000.0,
      "text": "Put like that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 226000.0,
      "end_time": 230699.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s easy to see why Edward Teach and his fellow pirates"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 230699.0,
      "end_time": 235198.0,
      "text": "could be seen as pioneers of modern communications design,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 235198.0,
      "end_time": 237146.0,
      "text": "and why their deadly symbol --"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 237146.0,
      "end_time": 238232.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 238232.0,
      "end_time": 239407.0,
      "text": "there&#39;s more --"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 239407.0,
      "end_time": 242416.0,
      "text": "why their deadly symbol of the skull and crossbones"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 242416.0,
      "end_time": 244730.0,
      "text": "was a precursor of today&#39;s logos,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 244730.0,
      "end_time": 248101.0,
      "text": "rather like the big red letters standing behind me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 248101.0,
      "end_time": 250304.0,
      "text": "but of course with a different message."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 250304.0,
      "end_time": 251332.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 251332.0,
      "end_time": 254366.0,
      "text": "Yet design was also used to nobler ends"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 254366.0,
      "end_time": 258604.0,
      "text": "by an equally brilliant and equally improbable designer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 258603.99999999997,
      "end_time": 262464.0,
      "text": "the 19th-century British nurse, Florence Nightingale."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 262464.0,
      "end_time": 267367.0,
      "text": "Her mission was to provide decent healthcare for everyone."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 267367.0,
      "end_time": 271807.0,
      "text": "Nightingale was born into a rather grand, very wealthy British family,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 271807.0,
      "end_time": 275872.0,
      "text": "who were horrified when she volunteered to work in military hospitals"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 275872.0,
      "end_time": 277963.0,
      "text": "during the Crimean War."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 277963.0,
      "end_time": 280316.0,
      "text": "Once there, she swiftly realized"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 280316.0,
      "end_time": 283953.0,
      "text": "that more patients were dying of infections that they caught there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 283953.0,
      "end_time": 285945.0,
      "text": "in the filthy, fetid wards,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 285945.0,
      "end_time": 287722.0,
      "text": "than they were of battle wounds."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 287722.0,
      "end_time": 292032.0,
      "text": "So she campaigned for cleaner, lighter, airier clinics"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 292032.0,
      "end_time": 294389.0,
      "text": "to be designed and built."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 294389.0,
      "end_time": 295598.0,
      "text": "Back in Britain,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 295598.0,
      "end_time": 297112.0,
      "text": "she mounted another campaign,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 297112.0,
      "end_time": 299194.0,
      "text": "this time for civilian hospitals,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 299194.0,
      "end_time": 303496.0,
      "text": "and insisted that the same design principles were applied to them."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 303496.0,
      "end_time": 306272.0,
      "text": "The Nightingale ward, as it is called,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 306272.0,
      "end_time": 309976.0,
      "text": "dominated hospital design for decades to come,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 309976.0,
      "end_time": 313834.0,
      "text": "and elements of it are still used today."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 313834.0,
      "end_time": 315113.0,
      "text": "But by then,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 315113.0,
      "end_time": 318165.0,
      "text": "design was seen as a tool of the Industrial Age."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 318165.0,
      "end_time": 320915.0,
      "text": "It was formalized and professionalized,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 320915.0,
      "end_time": 323432.0,
      "text": "but it was restricted to specific roles"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 323432.0,
      "end_time": 326534.0,
      "text": "and generally applied in pursuit of commercial goals"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 326534.0,
      "end_time": 328833.0,
      "text": "rather than being used intuitively,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 328833.0,
      "end_time": 333412.0,
      "text": "as Florence Nightingale, Blackbeard and Ying Zheng had done."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 333412.0,
      "end_time": 334906.0,
      "text": "By the 20th century,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 334906.0,
      "end_time": 337943.0,
      "text": "this commercial ethos was so powerful,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 337943.0,
      "end_time": 340491.0,
      "text": "that any designers who deviated from it"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 340491.0,
      "end_time": 344538.0,
      "text": "risked being seen as cranks or subversives."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 344538.0,
      "end_time": 348378.0,
      "text": "Now among them is one of my great design heroes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 348378.0,
      "end_time": 350930.0,
      "text": "the brilliant László Moholy-Nagy."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 350930.0,
      "end_time": 353721.0,
      "text": "He was the Hungarian artist and designer"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 353721.0,
      "end_time": 358001.0,
      "text": "whose experiments with the impact of technology on daily life"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 358001.0,
      "end_time": 359191.0,
      "text": "were so powerful"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 359191.0,
      "end_time": 362515.0,
      "text": "that they still influence the design of the digital images"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 362515.0,
      "end_time": 365658.0,
      "text": "we see on our phone and computer screens."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 365658.0,
      "end_time": 370379.0,
      "text": "He radicalized the Bauhaus Design School in 1920s Germany,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 370379.0,
      "end_time": 373150.0,
      "text": "and yet some of his former colleagues shunned him"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 373150.0,
      "end_time": 378194.0,
      "text": "when he struggled to open a new Bauhaus in Chicago years later."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 378194.0,
      "end_time": 382432.0,
      "text": "Moholy&#39;s ideas were as bold and incisive as ever,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 382432.0,
      "end_time": 386183.0,
      "text": "but his approach to design was too experimental,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 386183.0,
      "end_time": 389691.0,
      "text": "as was his insistence on seeing it, as he put it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 389691.0,
      "end_time": 394782.0,
      "text": "as an attitude, not a profession to be in tune with the times."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 394782.0,
      "end_time": 396659.0,
      "text": "And sadly, the same applied"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 396659.0,
      "end_time": 401167.0,
      "text": "to another design maverick: Richard Buckminster Fuller."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 401167.0,
      "end_time": 404881.0,
      "text": "He was yet another brilliant design visionary"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 404881.0,
      "end_time": 406322.0,
      "text": "and design activist,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 406322.0,
      "end_time": 410910.0,
      "text": "who was completely committed to designing a sustainable society"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 410910.0,
      "end_time": 412814.0,
      "text": "in such a forward-thinking way"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 412814.0,
      "end_time": 416178.0,
      "text": "that he started talking about the importance of environmentalism"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 416178.0,
      "end_time": 419632.0,
      "text": "in design in the 1920s."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 419632.0,
      "end_time": 422109.0,
      "text": "Now he, despite his efforts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 422109.0,
      "end_time": 426866.0,
      "text": "was routinely mocked as a crank by many in the design establishment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 426866.0,
      "end_time": 428058.0,
      "text": "and admittedly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 428058.0,
      "end_time": 429875.0,
      "text": "some of his experiments failed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 429875.0,
      "end_time": 432893.0,
      "text": "like the flying car that never got off the ground."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 432893.0,
      "end_time": 434965.0,
      "text": "And yet, the geodesic dome,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 434965.0,
      "end_time": 438313.0,
      "text": "his design formula to build an emergency shelter"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 438313.0,
      "end_time": 441018.0,
      "text": "from scraps of wood, metal, plastic,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 441018.0,
      "end_time": 444288.0,
      "text": "bits of tree, old blankets, plastic sheeting --"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 444288.0,
      "end_time": 447059.0,
      "text": "just about anything that&#39;s available at the time --"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 447059.0,
      "end_time": 450654.0,
      "text": "is one of the greatest feats of humanitarian design,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 450654.0,
      "end_time": 453341.0,
      "text": "and has provided sorely needed refuge"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 453341.0,
      "end_time": 456588.0,
      "text": "to many, many people in desperate circumstances"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 456588.0,
      "end_time": 458446.0,
      "text": "ever since."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 458446.0,
      "end_time": 462508.0,
      "text": "Now, it was the courage and verve of radical designers"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 462508.0,
      "end_time": 464384.0,
      "text": "like Bucky and Moholy"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 464384.0,
      "end_time": 466681.0,
      "text": "that drew me to design."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 466681.0,
      "end_time": 470741.0,
      "text": "I began my career as a news journalist and foreign correspondent."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 470741.0,
      "end_time": 474183.0,
      "text": "I wrote about politics, economics and corporate affairs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 474183.0,
      "end_time": 478033.0,
      "text": "and I could have chosen to specialize in any of those fields."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 478033.0,
      "end_time": 479801.0,
      "text": "But I picked design,"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 479801.0,
      "end_time": 483533.0,
      "text": "because I believe it&#39;s one of the most powerful tools at our disposal"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 483533.0,
      "end_time": 487755.0,
      "text": "to improve our quality of life."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 487755.0,
      "end_time": 490357.0,
      "text": "Thank you, fellow TED design buffs."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 490357.0,
      "end_time": 492045.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 492045.0,
      "end_time": 496477.0,
      "text": "And greatly as I admire the achievements of professional designers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 496477.0,
      "end_time": 499096.0,
      "text": "which have been extraordinary and immense,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 499096.0,
      "end_time": 500581.0,
      "text": "I also believe"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 500581.0,
      "end_time": 504098.0,
      "text": "that design benefits hugely from the originality,"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 504098.0,
      "end_time": 505440.0,
      "text": "the lateral thinking"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 505440.0,
      "end_time": 509683.0,
      "text": "and the resourcefulness of its rebels and renegades."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 509683.0,
      "end_time": 513653.0,
      "text": "And we&#39;re living at a remarkable moment in design,"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 513653.0,
      "end_time": 518481.0,
      "text": "because this is a time when the two camps are coming closer together."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 518481.0,
      "end_time": 522796.0,
      "text": "Because even very basic advances in digital technology"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 522796.00000000006,
      "end_time": 527104.0,
      "text": "have enabled them to operate increasingly independently,"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 527104.0,
      "end_time": 529542.0,
      "text": "in or out of a commercial context,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 529542.0,
      "end_time": 534615.0,
      "text": "to pursue ever more ambitious and eclectic objectives."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 534615.0,
      "end_time": 536285.0,
      "text": "So in theory,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 536285.0,
      "end_time": 541596.0,
      "text": "basic platforms like crowdfunding, cloud computing, social media"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 541596.0,
      "end_time": 545064.0,
      "text": "are giving greater freedom to professional designers"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 545064.0,
      "end_time": 548573.0,
      "text": "and giving more resources for the improvisational ones,"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 548573.0,
      "end_time": 549754.0,
      "text": "and hopefully,"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 549754.0,
      "end_time": 552671.0,
      "text": "a more receptive response to their ideas."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 552671.0,
      "end_time": 556862.0,
      "text": "Now, some of my favorite examples of this are in Africa,"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 556862.0,
      "end_time": 559013.0,
      "text": "where a new generation of designers"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 559013.0,
      "end_time": 562582.0,
      "text": "are developing incredible Internet of Things technologies"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 562582.0,
      "end_time": 567210.0,
      "text": "to fulfill Florence Nightingale&#39;s dream of improving healthcare"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 567210.0,
      "end_time": 570782.0,
      "text": "in countries where more people now have access to cell phones"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 570782.0,
      "end_time": 572991.0,
      "text": "than to clean, running water."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 572991.0,
      "end_time": 575642.0,
      "text": "And among them is Arthur Zang."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 575642.0,
      "end_time": 578536.0,
      "text": "He&#39;s a young, Cameroonian design engineer"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 578536.0,
      "end_time": 582705.0,
      "text": "who has a adapted a tablet computer into the Cardiopad,"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 582705.0,
      "end_time": 585152.0,
      "text": "a mobile heart-monitoring device."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 585152.0,
      "end_time": 589517.0,
      "text": "It can be used to monitor the hearts of patients in remote, rural areas."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 589517.0,
      "end_time": 592187.0,
      "text": "The data is then sent on a cellular network"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 592187.0,
      "end_time": 595241.0,
      "text": "to well-equipped hospitals hundreds of miles away"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 595241.0,
      "end_time": 596441.0,
      "text": "for analysis."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 596441.0,
      "end_time": 599770.0,
      "text": "And if any problems are spotted by the specialists there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 599770.0,
      "end_time": 603018.0,
      "text": "a suitable course of treatment is recommended."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 603018.0,
      "end_time": 605353.0,
      "text": "And this of course saves many patients"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 605353.0,
      "end_time": 610582.0,
      "text": "from making long, arduous, expensive and often pointless journeys"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 610582.0,
      "end_time": 611924.0,
      "text": "to those hospitals,"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 611924.0,
      "end_time": 614227.0,
      "text": "and makes it much, much likelier"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 614227.0,
      "end_time": 617298.0,
      "text": "that their hearts will actually be checked."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 617298.0,
      "end_time": 620644.0,
      "text": "Arthur Zang started working on the Cardiopad eight years ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 620644.0,
      "end_time": 623391.0,
      "text": "in his final year at university."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 623391.0,
      "end_time": 626830.0,
      "text": "But he failed to persuade any conventional sources"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 626830.0,
      "end_time": 630281.0,
      "text": "to give him investment to get the project off the ground."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 630281.0,
      "end_time": 632178.0,
      "text": "He posted the idea on Facebook,"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 632178.0,
      "end_time": 634858.0,
      "text": "where a Cameroonian government official saw it"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 634858.0,
      "end_time": 638119.0,
      "text": "and managed to secure a government grant for him."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 638119.0,
      "end_time": 641179.0,
      "text": "He&#39;s now developing not only the Cardiopad,"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 641179.0,
      "end_time": 645831.0,
      "text": "but other mobile medical devices to treat different conditions."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 645831.0,
      "end_time": 647501.0,
      "text": "And he isn&#39;t alone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 647501.0,
      "end_time": 652448.0,
      "text": "because there are many other inspiring and enterprising designers"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 652448.0,
      "end_time": 656364.0,
      "text": "who are also pursuing extraordinary projects of their own."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 656364.0,
      "end_time": 659934.0,
      "text": "And I&#39;m going to finish by looking at just a few of them."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 659934.0,
      "end_time": 662213.0,
      "text": "One is Peek Vision."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 662213.0,
      "end_time": 665312.0,
      "text": "This is a group of doctors and designers in Kenya,"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 665312.0,
      "end_time": 668545.0,
      "text": "who&#39;ve developed an Internet of Things technology of their own,"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 668545.0,
      "end_time": 671639.0,
      "text": "as a portable eye examination kit."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 671639.0,
      "end_time": 673585.0,
      "text": "Then there&#39;s Gabriel Maher,"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 673585.0,
      "end_time": 675683.0,
      "text": "who is developing a new design language"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 675683.0,
      "end_time": 680827.0,
      "text": "to enable us to articulate the subtleties of our changing gender identities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 680827.0,
      "end_time": 683736.0,
      "text": "without recourse to traditional stereotypes."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 683736.0,
      "end_time": 688027.0,
      "text": "All of these designers and many more are pursuing their dreams,"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 688027.0,
      "end_time": 690677.0,
      "text": "by the making the most of their newfound freedom,"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 690677.0,
      "end_time": 693599.0,
      "text": "with the discipline of professional designers"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 693599.0,
      "end_time": 696525.0,
      "text": "and the resourcefulness of rebels and renegades."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 696525.0,
      "end_time": 698611.0,
      "text": "And we all stand to benefit."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 698611.0,
      "end_time": 699798.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 699798.0,
      "end_time": 709798.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}